{"tid":199924,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［連登法庭］上網買野比人呃","createTime":"2017-04-13T14:20:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T11:53:54.000Z","uid":105868,"like":78,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"16740cd8da26c3150c936b3093a83d9a4893dae3","tid":199924,"uid":105868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T14:20:20.000Z","msg":"前兩星期係上網買左野，過左900蚊比條友，但之後發現有幾個人留言話佢呃錢冇貨比，之後都收唔到貨，就同條友講退錢，次次搵親條撚樣都話唔得閒過唔到數。<br />\n之後幾個受害者都收到佢聲稱ebanking入左數既cap圖，但最後都冇人收過退錢，但佢會照聽電話照應whatsapp。<br />\n過左幾個星期，我同幾個受害者警都報埋，但警察唔肯開file查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同佢講報左警，條撚樣都係唔撚識驚，覺得告唔撚到佢，就繼續拖，日日就扮撚哂好忙咁撚樣。<br />\n<br />\n雖然900蚊話多唔多，話少唔少，錢預左冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但真係好憎人呃鳩人錢，起撚左條友底，既然報警佢都唔撚驚，希望連登法庭幫手懲罰下呢啲仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/13/221033_811dcd471a7d4fff55dcaeef9b3f1c55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F13%2F221033_811dcd471a7d4fff55dcaeef9b3f1c55.jpg&h=d21265aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6c6U2Fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6c6U2Fb.jpg&h=142e6086&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後佢扮撚哂受害者咁，仲歡迎大家向佢退款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但仍然冇退過<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/13/221419_400437b1fc9131ee445b549391491294.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F13%2F221419_400437b1fc9131ee445b549391491294.jpg&h=8539331c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e25T9AR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe25T9AR.jpg&h=3404a847&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/13/221421_779abdfacd5d7d4506a97df558f57ce3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F13%2F221421_779abdfacd5d7d4506a97df558f57ce3.jpg&h=56fa749c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/13/221422_779abdfacd5d7d4506a97df558f57ce3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F13%2F221422_779abdfacd5d7d4506a97df558f57ce3.jpg&h=b5b3c33e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n電話：6888 8549<br />\n<br />\n法官大人們，可以點樣懲罰呢啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeaddd51ca7fbb5379f11b58f150ebe39823dbd6","tid":199924,"uid":105868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T14:27:00.000Z","msg":"推<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d5f87efdc50dffca0054b8ae22337702b68288","tid":199924,"uid":105868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T14:28:43.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2321bd9beb9bfdbfa177b7bb2d875d311a8ed91f","tid":199924,"uid":97451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T14:31:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3eb6d43f74e4ce0f635f8511f689f72cd89c5f2c","tid":199924,"uid":105868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T14:35:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>報警都有用既，如果每個受害者都無收貨紀錄就可以告，希望巴打可以捉到條友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n報左啦，差佬話仲聯絡到佢告唔到佢詐騙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aca97a95b4fc28b1bfccae6009e36f42c38a167","tid":199924,"uid":105868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T14:45:16.000Z","msg":"繼續推"},{"pid":"1fdf48585c4d2d232ea030ad1137b303ab6d8e9a","tid":199924,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"